collections.name: Wine Ladies
collections.description:
Discover the magic of Wine Ladies: a unique collection that combines the power of wine to describe female world. 🍷✍️ As a wine artist specialized in wine communication, I’ve fused these two passions to offer you an extraordinary experience. Let every glass tell a story! 
The Wine Ladies collection tells the story of a woman and her many facets. Different personalities, different traits—everything that makes a woman unique begins with a stain of wine. From here, the creative process unfolds, transforming from abstract to figurative art. And so, we discover the lightness of the Dancer, the beauty of the Mother, a hint of mischief in the Sexy and the Lolita, the fun of the Rocker, and the rebellious spirit of the Bad Girl.
